  <li>Designed and developed web application for tracking asbestos waste shipment records for construction projects at the University. System allows the University to track regulatory compliance dates and ensure all asbestos waste is disposed at Harvard approved disposal sites in an appropriate manner and timeframe.</li>
  <li>2006 Harvard Heroes honoree: for leadership, teamwork, adaptability, and work that set new standards for performance at Harvard University.</li>
